# Agentic Commerce Stack — Starter Template

This template is a complete, working starter kit for the full protocol stack: **MCP**, **A2A**, **UCP**, **ACP**, and **AP2**.

## Services

| Service | Port | What it does |
|---|---|---|
| `chat-client` | 3000 | React UI + Protocol Inspector |
| `merchant-agent` | 10999 | Merchant agent with A2A, UCP checkout, AP2 token, and `/ws/trace` |
| `mcp-server` | 8001 | MCP tools over an inline sample catalog |

## Run locally

```bash
cp .env.example .env
docker-compose up --build
```

For area-specific guidance, use the rules for `merchant-agent`, `mcp-server`, `chat-client`, and `evals`.
